---
title: BBQ Pulled Chicken Tacos & CholulaⓇ Slaw with Cilantro
description: Dreaming up ways to spice up taco night? Look no further: This mashup version delivers all the flavors of a summer cookout, no grill required. Pulled barbecue chicken is tossed with sautéed onion and lime juice to form the saucy filling. It’s stuffed into warm tortillas with a creamy, spicy slaw for crunchy contrast. Plus, it’s all ready in just 15 minutes—taco ’bout a dinner winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bbq-pulled-chicken-tacos-cholula-slaw-9971b2fe.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/bbq-pulled-chicken-tacos-cholula-slaw-605a5cc4932040538e75dd5b-8bfc24d4.pdf
time required: 15 minutes
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/bbq-pulled-chicken-tacos-and-cholula-slaw-605a5cc4932040538e75dd5b
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 720 kcal
